n matching engine with Starknet settlement. The funding payment occurs between long and short positions based on the rate differential between perpetual and spot prices. Cross-margin support allows traders to efficiently manage multiple positions while zero gas fees eliminate transaction costs that typically eat into funding rate profits. The fast execution engine ensures minimal slippage when entering or exiting arbitrage positions."}]]}],"$Lf",["$L10","$L11","$L12"],"$L13"]}],"$L14"]}]]}]
